snippet.title: "I hate him" Johnny Depp reveals he still hates Elon Musk after his affair with Amber Heard
snippet.description:
💙 "I hate him" Johnny Depp reveals he still hates Elon Musk after his affair with Amber Heard
So Elon musk and amber heard, both agree they had an affair, but the timing of this mentioned by them is after Amber’s divorce, though the evidence proves otherwise.
Who would not want to kill a man who steals away their wife, right?
Some may say that Johnny’s anger is reasonable so before we jump to conclusions, let me show you a bigger picture.
Before Johnny receives his official divorce from Amber, he accuses her of infidelity.
